title: Tila Tequila
description:
Tila Tequila, written by Caitlin Tegart. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, April 14, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, D'Arcy Erokan & Fran Gillespie. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
